3 proposed constitutional amendment submitted by the general
4 assembly, by initiative petition, or by constitutional
5 convention, or for a statutory initiative or referendum
6 measure, may bring an action in the circuit court of Cole
7 County. The action [must] shall be brought within ten days

SB 1615 9
8 after the official ballot title is certified by the
